{"tid":2498373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實根據支那小粉紅平時嘅準則，Marvel套尚氣係辱華到仆街","createTime":"2021-04-21T06:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T06:26:02.000Z","uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"84b723da24151867c13a869449c792f1f103bc73","tid":2498373,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T06:14:31.000Z","msg":"演員已經辱華<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRrw1T6Hhi5GcwpShNeUmrvVrtTZTw9S1yjRnrgYBPH2N?filename=pTTvF3C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpTTvF3C.png&h=019fe559&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRdR5rYdqg4Xn3PLhJeggr5enRYhCCttW21AuzBKceBPz?filename=Jt65u4y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJt65u4y.jpg&h=cef6aea3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n撞樣翠翠嘅主角<br />\n同支共啲高官一樣<br />\n支那出世但外套護照<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmakSz353c66LvFi2hsMxbSkb89ByuT4jbbUG56Hcwy8Dx?filename=mc43gCZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmc43gCZ.png&h=16581a87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對家係靚仔過佢好撚多嘅梁朝偉<br />\n英籍香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ntrailer啲對白都可以辱華<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPozPznm1M2ft1AjMp6vkGnfLg23T6nFzkb1Jfut5M4WJ?filename=mhso05W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmhso05W.png&h=84ba8607&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcerY3TH7caDWZZz1AMKux5R22YDqpuffcqsPUNEGcGug?filename=VNhcUqX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNhcUqX.png&h=69cf39d0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTH9KpT4RphSPLqkk5qSXCp2e8kxL1UhRKtPLsK6vs8Yp?filename=fuj3gEi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffuj3gEi.png&h=e090fc6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n支那過咗咁多年都仲要靠香港呢隻白手套<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYYR5zNSMYD6Q8BPPpgjpD2UEgnfiMsREkRqSZdYazMxy?filename=Ea0YP0K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEa0YP0K.png&h=ca546b05&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVFuFAfyY1cmNbNgA9QVdG5QwBP6jbSKDiTZuSjnC3G2h?filename=H2m9cd7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH2m9cd7.png&h=6c6b20a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdhrMDZQkmq4K4ydShNgvJ2WMxUNfJtorC6rjGkwEthkm?filename=WT9yDUa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWT9yDUa.png&h=1cece359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁朝偉係主角個老豆<br />\n香港都早過共產黨出現<br />\n支那可以話係食香港嘅奶粉大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZTSyZxCcsbESVRofjLAzEdUUqA7cjMUkW8GwxLK4Ngni?filename=bb0eom0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbb0eom0.jpg&h=6b05f644&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最重要係梁朝偉型撚過主角太多<br />\n大部分人都話似翠翠嘅主角唔撚掂成個路人咁，係咁屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMarvel呢次選角真係錯撚哂<br />\n一係你唔好簡個似翠翠嘅演員<br />\n一係你就簡個唔好咁撚型嘅反派啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個戲名又撚柒，比人話尚氣唔接下氣<br />\n小粉紅出征未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVAhcq3tQFU1tqXYvgQj96HjWcydDNmLHN58guyFy4NC8?filename=YDQqu4K.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYDQqu4K.gif&h=473d6099&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ee7de42dc4be0de63c0947f0682b4e86712badd","tid":2498373,"uid":70527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T06:20:20.000Z","msg":"仲有個女主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e089f03b2cc0a7709673074ba90c198e913f63","tid":2498373,"uid":82068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T06:26:02.000Z","msg":"英屬香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}